        "class": "",
        "text": "(k) \"in loca tenebrosa\", Tigurine version, Musculus; \"in tenebrosissimis\", Junius & Tremellius; \"in densis tenebris\", Piscator; \"in caligines, vel obscuritates\", Gejerus. (l) Descriptio Africae, l. 3. p. 413. ",
        "children": [
          {
